---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`关于 - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="关于本站的介绍" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Navigation />
		<div class="desktop">
			<div class="window">
				<div class="title-bar">
					<div class="title-bar-text">关于本站</div>
				</div>
				<div class="window-body">
					<h2>关于本站</h2>
					<p>这是微信公众号“摸鱼的小灰栗”的公网版本站点，使用 Astro 框架构建，采用 98.css 实现怀旧的 Windows 98 风格界面。</p>
					
					<h3>技术栈</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Astro - 静态站点生成器</li>
						<li>98.css - Windows 98 风格的 CSS 框架</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
	</div>
	<Footer />
</body>
</html>

<style>
	html, body {
		height: 100%;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}
	
	body {
		background: #c0c0c0;
		font-family: 'MS Sans Serif', sans-serif;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}
	
	.desktop {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 20px;
		flex: 1;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}
	
	.window {
		flex: 1;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}
	
	.window-body {
		flex: 1;
		padding: 20px;
	}
	
	h2, h3 {
		color: #000080;
		margin: 20px 0 10px 0;
	}
	
	p, li {
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 10px 0;
	}
	
	ul {
		padding-left: 20px;
	}
</style>